# 9. Developer Logic Summary

### Trial Start


StartTrial(plan):
  Create trial subscription
  Set trial_end = now + 7 days
  Assign trial_points
  Activate trial_permissions


### Trial Active State


If now < trial_end:
  trial_active = true
Else:
  trial_active = false


### Feature Lock Logic


If trial_active AND feature not in trial_permissions:
    Block + Show Upgrade Modal


### Trial Expiry


If now >= trial_end:
   Pause campaigns
   Lock points
   Lock editing
   Show upgrade screen


